# Features covered: HTML parser
#
# This file contains a collection of tests for the HTML parser.
# Tested functionalities:
#    html5-1.*: Character encoding
#    html5-2.*: Parsing tests
#    html5-3.*: Bad data
#    html5-4.*: DOM building
